        </item>
        <item>
            <title>的士司機周街大叫「無微信啊」兼爆粗，網民：疑後車投訴前車藉「無微信」拒載短途客</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=taxinowechatpay</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 06:25:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[的士]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1238232</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>的士司機服務態度與是否應該支援電子支付成為近日熱門話題。而昨晚網上更爆出一段短片成為熱話，影片中司機在街上一個的士站落車不斷重覆狂叫「無微信啊！」兼狂爆粗口。網民質疑，片中司機藉「無微信」而拒載短途客，將短途客塞向後車，令後車司機不滿而口角。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1238233 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024052622016-394x580.jpg" alt="" width="394" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024052622016-394x580.jpg 394w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024052622016.jpg 611w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 394px" /></p><p>昨晚 Facebook 羣組「車 cam L（香港羣組）」有網民發佈一段短片，影片中司機不斷狂叫「無微信啊」引起途人矚目。影片一開始，看到的士站排第二的後車司機，走向前車司機面前投訴。而前車司機開始發難，在街上狂叫「無微信啊 XX，XXXX，XXX，微信啊無微信丫嘛！無微信啊，無微信丫嘛！無微信啊！XXXX！無微信啊！&#8230;.XXX，無微信點收錢啊，又話我黑的，咁大個牌寫住收現金家嘛」。</p><p>影片看到前車司機非常重視其「無微信」的立場，與後方司機在街頭口角。網民懷疑，後方司機投訴，是因為前車司機拒載疑似短途客，雙方因而口角。而前車司機理直壯以「無微信」為由推掉乘客到後車。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1238239" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240526_2_32_51-694x327.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="327" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240526_2_32_51-694x327.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240526_2_32_51.jpg 798w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>近日網約車、的士服務態度成為熱話，政府已經邀請有興趣人士成立的士車隊，希望透過更優質管理，以及能夠收取電子支付、能夠網約的士，多方面為市民遊客提供更好的服務。對於的士是否支援電子支付，市民與司機雙方仍然存在分岐，後者認為電子支付需要繳付手續費，相關交易亦會被記錄，引入電子支付的司機仍然只佔極少數。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyeeyee.lam.104%2Fvideos%2F1360890721272956%2F%3Fidorvanity%3D857985435068408&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=269&amp;t=0" width="269" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1360890721272956">車 cam L（香港羣組）Facebook 專頁</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/online-ride-hailing/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">黃鳳嫺再倡網約車合法化，若的士車隊制未能滿足市民將再提</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/21/a-14-year-old-is-charged-in-fire-that-destroyed-a-driverless-waymo-vehicle/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">三藩市自動駕駛的士縱火案有進展　14 歲疑犯被起訴</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/10/taxi-team-5/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">的士車隊牌照週五起接受申請　最多發 5 牌照 + 車隊可自訂預訂行程收費</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/">的士司機周街大叫「無微信啊」兼爆粗，網民：疑後車投訴前車藉「無微信」拒載短途客</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
